{"tid":331870,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"（有圖）前中國女排重炮手王一梅 減磅靚到唔認得！！！","createTime":"2017-07-22T13:54:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T05:14:37.000Z","uid":5812,"like":9,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a540f86c31f0e8b4f37125c7f442d0748dc2cbba","tid":331870,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T13:54:19.000Z","msg":"世界女排大獎香港站正進行得如火如荼，不少球迷都入場為中國女排打氣。這幾年朱婷就聽得多啦，但大家還記不記得當年有重炮手之稱的王一梅？以前睇開中國女排的都知道王一梅一直都是「有肉地」，但現年29歲的王一梅已經今時不同往日啦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/07/20170722_%E7%8E%8B%E4%B8%80%E6%A2%85_4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F07%2F20170722_%25E7%258E%258B%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%25A2%2585_4.jpg&h=0767cc35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n份量十足的王一梅曾經是中國女排的重炮手之一，在排球場上力量型殺波令不少對手好有威脅感。近年已經淡出國家隊，但王一梅仍然有繼續打排球㗎！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/07/20170722_%E7%8E%8B%E4%B8%80%E6%A2%85.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F07%2F20170722_%25E7%258E%258B%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%25A2%2585.jpg&h=db9739e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/07/20170722_%E7%8E%8B%E4%B8%80%E6%A2%85_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F07%2F20170722_%25E7%258E%258B%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%25A2%2585_2.jpg&h=c108c5b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/07/20170722_%E7%8E%8B%E4%B8%80%E6%A2%85_3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F07%2F20170722_%25E7%258E%258B%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%25A2%2585_3.jpg&h=0da2c52c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過球迷就發現現時的王一梅與在國家隊時明顯不同，她已經不是以前的她，講緊的是身材！王一梅成功減磅，更加瘦到變瓜子臉，靚樣「出晒嚟」!她還不時在微博分享自己的生活照及靚靚自拍照！"},{"pid":"0935406e1a624f46ae2b616b3b50fa6458debe2f","tid":331870,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T13:57:37.000Z","msg":"三個連登仔合體都唔夠佢高"},{"pid":"9786c20695b589eff5199b06ce2e12f5c9971bf5","tid":331870,"uid":47893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T13:59:59.000Z","msg":"係真唔係佢呀 ？ 靚左咁多"},{"pid":"cdd4564abf771e46da19116c8c42addc21283b53","tid":331870,"uid":118656,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:00:01.000Z","msg":"以前正好多 好想比佢一掌轟落條野到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b903029dac38bf6f16749391aef925b6528c6ab9","tid":331870,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:01:41.000Z","msg":"個下爬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d41ff55fa11f869a5129e5c07e0e2ff2985928dc","tid":331870,"uid":48448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:09:12.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"037c45f6dbca114a3b5233d4cdd0c5dc863c9f38","tid":331870,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:12:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/zmZPl8D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FzmZPl8D.jpg&h=bfb4b6be&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c0eaa57a18007c91842b5a7dcc1611c9b9e6b2b9","tid":331870,"uid":36238,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:14:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母</blockquote><br />\n唔岩睇咪唔好睇囉 郁d講人老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52bd0d6dfc7b9535f8a64f23fa6ac63f03dbc0ea","tid":331870,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:15:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個下爬<img src=\"